OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776250558
OL,3,CHow doing your washing at weekends
OL,4,Ccould get you a discount on your
OL,5,Celectricity
OL,7,FAre you one of the households that
OL,8,Fcould benefit, and what is the reason
OL,9,Fbehind the perk? ITV News explains.
OL,11,FWho are NESO?
OL,13,FThe National Energy System Operator,
OL,14,Fknown as Neso, is the public body
OL,15,Fresponsible for managing and planning
OL,16,Fthe UK's electricity and gas networks.
OL,18,FNeso works to help the UK government
OL,19,Fto "achieve its net zero target" and
OL,20,F"ensure the security of energy supply
OL,21,Ffor consumers."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776250558
OL,3,CHow doing your washing at weekends
OL,4,Ccould get you a discount on your
OL,5,Celectricity
OL,7,FIt also works to "promote the
OL,8,Fefficient and economical transmission
OL,9,Fand distribution of electricity and
OL,10,Fgas".
OL,12,FThe operator runs a scheme called the
OL,13,FDemand Flexibility Service, which
OL,14,Frewards consumers and businesses for
OL,15,Fadapting when they use power, if the
OL,16,Fenergy system needs support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
