PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776250558
OL,3,CHow doing your washing at weekends
OL,4,Ccould get you a discount on your
OL,5,Celectricity
OL,7,FBy taking part in the service,
OL,8,Fconsumers "help balance the
OL,9,Felectricity system, reduce overall
OL,10,Fcosts, and support a cleaner, more
OL,11,Fefficient energy system."
OL,13,FThis summer, the scheme will now
OL,14,Freward households and businesses for
OL,15,Fincreasing their electricity use
OL,16,Fduring periods of excess supply due to
OL,17,Fweather conditions.
OL,19,FWhy are consumers being rewarded?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
