CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776250558
OL,3,CHow doing your washing at weekends
OL,4,Ccould get you a discount on your
OL,5,Celectricity
OL,7,FThe system requires monitoring all day
OL,8,Feveryday; "If things fall out of
OL,9,Fbalance, the frequency drops, voltage
OL,10,Fdrops, and we will see power cuts ` so
OL,11,Fwe can never allow this to happen."
OL,13,FDr Deborah Petterson from Neso says,
OL,14,F"The work of our excellent engineering
OL,15,Fteams at NESO means our energy system
OL,16,Fis well adapted to support a clean,
OL,17,Fresilient future, and puts us in a
OL,18,Fstrong position to manage the changing
OL,19,Fpatterns of electricity use over the
OL,20,Fsummer.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
