OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776250558
OL,3,CHow doing your washing at weekends
OL,4,Ccould get you a discount on your
OL,5,Celectricity
OL,7,FTools such as the Demand Flexibility
OL,8,FService not only reward consumers and
OL,9,Fbusinesses for flexible electricity
OL,10,Fuse but also strengthen the resilience
OL,11,Fand efficiency of Great Britain's
OL,12,Felectricity network."
OL,14,FHow does the reward scheme work?
OL,16,FWhen electricity demand is
OL,17,Fparticularly low, which is likely over
OL,18,Fthe sunny, windy weekends and bank
OL,19,Fholidays, Neso is able to reward
OL,20,Fcustomers who adapt their use of
OL,21,Felectricity.
OL,26,@tD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
