OL,3,CHow doing your washing at weekends
OL,4,Ccould get you a discount on your
OL,5,Celectricity
OL,7,FRunning household appliances such as
OL,8,Fwashing machines and dishwashers, or
OL,9,Fcharging electric cars during these
OL,10,Ftimes when there is an excess of
OL,11,Felectricity and lower demand, makes
OL,12,Fbetter use of the clean electricity
OL,13,Fwhich has already been generated.
OL,15,FNeso will let your energy supplier
OL,16,Fknow when a Demand Flexibility Service
OL,17,Fevent is due to take place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
