OL,3,CHow doing your washing at weekends
OL,4,Ccould get you a discount on your
OL,5,Celectricity
OL,7,FYour supplier will then contact you to
OL,8,Ftell you when the event is taking
OL,9,Fplace, as well as how long it will
OL,10,Flast.
OL,12,FThe scheme is open to those with smart
OL,13,Fmeters who are with providers that are
OL,14,Fsigned up to the scheme.
OL,16,FThe type and value of the rewards will
OL,17,Fvary depending on the provider.
OL,19,FWhich providers are part of the Demand
OL,20,FFlexibility Service?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
